  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate whether a multimodal rehabilitation program
      effectively reduces functional disability in adolescents with chronic musculoskeletal pain,
      compared to care as usual.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
